_even_wrong\" rel=\"nofollow\">not even wrong!<\/a> I&#39;d make the argument that this question is not well formed, nor do I see the possibility for a constructive outcome because OPs premise is wildly ignorant. Check OP&#39;s other questions- every one is a a variation on the same theme. None are useful and none are resolved. This is question is simply persistent noise."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/1MUb2.png?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":1306,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/1306/terdon","reputation":9339,"display_name":"terdon","accept_rate":73},"score":0,"post_id":16106,"reply_to_user":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4fd20b85d98a142f6c2f47ab7fd9bfb0?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":6131,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/6131/adamwong246","reputation":261,"display_name":"adamwong246"},"edited":false,"creation_date":1395872287,"comment_id":21672,"body":"@adamwong246 that&#39;s irrelevant. Remember that the SE sites are wikis and the information we give should not be aimed at the OP alone. The basic misconceptions here can be addressed, I&#39;ve tried to do so in my answer. As I&#39;m sure you know creationist and ID arguments tend to be ridiculously easy to shoot down, just like this one is. We should welcome the chance to do so in the hope that we might increase the understanding, if not of the OP, then of the next poor misguided soul who has fallen under the influence of pseudoscience."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4fd20b85d98a142f6c2f47ab7fd9bfb0?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":6131,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/6131/adamwong246","reputation":261,"display_name":"adamwong246"},"score":0,"post_id":16106,"edited":false,"creation_date":1395872418,"comment_id":21673,"body":"Perhaps this should be moved to a meta-discussion but is there really a hope that OP will ever select one of 