e or two ago, that's pretty darn good.<\/p>\n","answer_id":5655,"question_id":5587,"up_vote_count":3},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/463a98a64c97ea34800782ab7b61bb05?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":3262,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/3262/neodevlin","reputation":300,"display_name":"NeoDevlin"},"score":4,"is_accepted":false,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fe87113ced5f370d038b90a43fd1fe1f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":408,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/408/anixx","reputation":909,"display_name":"Anixx","accept_rate":20},"score":0,"post_id":7584,"edited":false,"creation_date":1363737901,"comment_id":9466,"body":"Is not it the same as post-exposure prophylactic, which is used if a surgeon or a dentist get wounded when performing operation on a HIV patient? I know that one can be cured if the treatment is started within 48 hours after infection."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fe87113ced5f370d038b90a43fd1fe1f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":408,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/408/anixx","reputation":909,"display_name":"Anixx","accept_rate":20},"score":0,"post_id":7584,"edited":false,"creation_date":1363738233,"comment_id":9467,"body":"It seems what is important is whether the latent reservoirs were established."},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/463a98a64c97ea34800782ab7b61bb05?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":3262,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/3262/neodevlin","reputation":300,"display_name":"NeoDevlin"},"score":0,"post_id":7584,"reply_to_user":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/fe87113ced5f370d038b90a43fd1fe1f?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":408,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/408/anixx","reputation":909,"display_name":"Anix