follow\">YAP suppression has been linked to cancerous growth<\/a>.  <a href=\"http://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/65/17/7561.full\" rel=\"nofollow\">And its also been shown that YAP is amplified in oral squamous cell carcinoma cells<\/a>.  This last is circumstantial but consistent with what we know about YAP. <\/p>\n","answer_id":10384,"question_id":10364,"up_vote_count":1},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/4594178aa0b95e1c164ab5fe9c16a4df?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG&f=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":4351,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/4351/researcher","reputation":1,"display_name":"Researcher"},"score":-1,"is_accepted":false,"comments":[{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/de2c4fd753821f85c74d886aa17410de?s=128&d=identicon&r=PG","user_type":"registered","user_id":107,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/107/kmm","reputation":8486,"display_name":"kmm"},"score":3,"post_id":10568,"edited":false,"creation_date":1380075412,"comment_id":14020,"body":"Could you expand on your answer with additional information and/or citations?"}],"down_vote_count":1,"last_activity_date":1380075031,"creation_date":1380075031,"body":"<p>Hippo Signal may affect the turnover rate of oral mucosa<\/p>\n","answer_id":10568,"question_id":10364,"up_vote_count":0}],"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/questions/10364/what-is-the-role-of-hippo-signalling-in-oral-squamous-cells","last_activity_date":1395637085,"creation_date":1378815323,"answer_count":2,"title":"What is the role of hippo signalling in oral squamous cells","body":"<p>What role do hippo signalling have on squamous cells in oral health &amp; diseases<\/p>\n","question_id":10364,"tags":["genetics"],"score":2,"down_vote_count":0,"is_answered":true,"view_count":55,"up_vote_count":2},{"owner":{"profile_image":"https://i.stack.imgur.com/3BSnX.jpg?s=128&g=1","user_type":"registered","user_id":4929,"link":"http://biology.stackexchange.com/users/4929/nicole-ra